events.name: EV Battery Supply Chain
events.wd_description: The EV battery supply chain consists of three main parts: cell manufacturing, module manufacturing, and pack assembly, which can be conducted in the same or different locations.

events.wd_description: The process of producing battery cells, which can be done in specialized facilities or as part of a larger battery production plant.

events.name: Module Manufacturing
